lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth featured in a six-ball on his last green in fading light at the Abu Dhabi Championship on Saturday as he became one of the few golfers to finish a fog-interrupted third round.

headline.print_headline: Spieth Beats Fading Light to Narrow Deficit in Abu Dhabi
